Origin
------
The VOUCH protocol concept — pre-call mutual identity verification using
Mobile ID, OmniOne Open DID, OmniOne Chain, and AI intent disclosure —
was conceived and architected by David Seo in May 2026 and first submitted
as a hackathon proposal on 2026-05-31.

This repository (github.com/gem-squared/gem2-ZTCV-advance) is the
authoritative public origin of the VOUCH protocol specification and its
reference Go implementation.

